I had to add a new function to Template.php, as my replacement names were totaly splitted in the XML source.
This function gives me an associative array with the replacement variable as key and the "true" string in the XML as value - In the setValue call i then replace this "true" string (there are no changes to the setValue function):

public function getReplacements() {
	$search = '/\${.*?.*?}/';

	$matches = array();
	preg_match_all($search, $this->_documentXML, $matches);

	$result = array();
	foreach($matches as $match) {
		foreach($match as $key => $value) {

			$result[trim(strip_tags($value), '${}')] = $value;

		}
	}

	return $result;

}
